OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Foccasional showers at first becoming
OL,7,Flargely dry overnight with clear
OL,8,Fperiods, especially towards the east.
OL,9,FWinds slowly easing with some patchy
OL,10,Ffrost possible by dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FChilly start, then bright
OL,13,Fspells through the morning but cloud
OL,14,Fthickens through the afternoon,
OL,15,Fperhaps with some patchy light rain
OL,16,Freaching the Pennines later. Winds
OL,17,Fincreasing by the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
