OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FSaturday, early rain followed by sunny
OL,7,Fspells and scattered blustery showers.
OL,8,FBreezy. Sunday, breezy with occasional
OL,9,Fblustery showers. Monday, fewer
OL,10,Fshowers and lighter winds.
OL,11,FTemperatures mostly around average.
